window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I haven't seen him since that night I gave him my V-card. He's got big plans for me because now he's my boss </b><b><i>and</i></b><b> my fake fiancé.</b></p> <p>Jackson:</p> <p>I had no choice but to disappear that night. It ripped my frickin' heart out.</p> <p>Now I'm moving my headquarters to Boulder with one objective: Win Mandy back. Damn, this is going to be hard.</p> <p>She's feisty and sassy and doesn't obey my orders. She wears short skirts on purpose—just to drive me wild.</p> <p>My dark past is following me. This fake engagement will keep her safe. But I'll show her how real my love is.</p> <p>My lips on hers. Between the sheets. Her screaming my name.</p> <p>Baby, I'll do whatever it takes to protect you. And I'll be damned if I let them separate us again.</p> <p>Big &amp; Bossy <i>is book one of the swoon-worthy Boulder Billionaires series and can be enjoyed as a standalone. Jackson and Mandy's steamy story will give you all the right feels. HEA? You bet!</i></p>"; 
